Description: Provides tools for qualitative analysis of one- and
    two-dimensional autonomous ordinary differential equation (ODE) systems
    using phase plane methods. Produces publication-quality visualisations
    via ggplot2 and its extensions. Functions are available to plot flow
    fields, nullclines, trajectories, phase portraits, and stable/unstable
    manifolds, and to identify and classify equilibrium points. A successor
    to the phaseR package (Grayling, 2014) <doi:10.32614/RJ-2014-023>.
